'''社会主义联盟'''（{{lang-en|Socialist Alliance}}）是[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]的一个[[左翼|左翼]]政党联盟（拥有注册政党地位）。该联盟成立于2006年，由5个政党组成：[[斯里兰卡共产党|斯里兰卡共产党]]、[[民主左翼阵线|民主左翼阵线]]、[[兰卡平等社会党|兰卡平等社会党]]、[[民族解放人民党|民族解放人民党]]和[[斯里兰卡人民党|斯里兰卡人民党]]。该联盟的秘书长是{{le|拉贾·科罗尔|Raja Collure}}。该联盟是[[统一人民自由联盟|统一人民自由联盟]]的成员<ref>{{cite news|last1=Perera|first1=Yohan|title=The rise and rise of another Alliance|url=http://archives.dailymirror.lk/2006/04/21/news/11.asp|work=The Daily Mirror|date=21 April 2006}}{{Dead link|date=2020年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Gnanadass|first1=Wilson|title=UNP, SLFP must arrive at consensus|url=http://www.nation.lk/2006/08/13/inter3.htm|work=The Nation|date=13 August 2006|accessdate=2020-04-21|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090954/http://www.nation.lk/2006/08/13/inter3.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Satyapalan|first1=Franklin R.|title=Dew: Socialist Alliance for struggle against neo-liberalism|url=http://www.island.lk/2006/04/23/news20.html|work=The Island|date=23 April 2006|accessdate=2020-04-21|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081637/http://www.island.lk/2006/04/23/news20.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Kurugala|first1=Priyanka|title=Socialist Alliance pledges to defeat UNP at General elections|url=http://www.dailynews.lk/?q=political/socialist-alliance-pledges-defeat-unp-general-elections|work=Daily News|date=11 July 2015|access-date=2020-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717131352/http://www.dailynews.lk/?q=political%2Fsocialist-alliance-pledges-defeat-unp-general-elections|archive-date=2015-07-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Socialist Alliance unhappy over nominees|url=http://www.ceylontoday.lk/51-10039-news-detail-socialist-alliance-unhappy-over-nominees.html|work=Ceylon Today|date=23 July 2012|access-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093802/http://www.ceylontoday.lk/51-100